import React from 'react'; const About = () => (

About Me

I am currently pursuing an MBA in Hospital Administration and Healthcare Management (HAHM) from the Indian Institute of Management Jammu. This program equips me with advanced knowledge and skills to manage complex healthcare systems efficiently, combining business management principles with healthcare expertise.

With a passion for healthcare management, I am focused on developing leadership abilities and strategic insights to contribute effectively to the evolving healthcare sector. My academic journey is complemented by practical case studies and real-world applications, preparing me to tackle challenges in hospital administration, quality assurance, and healthcare consulting.

Skills & Interests

  • Healthcare Systems Management
  • Hospital Operations & Quality Assurance
  • Business Strategy & Finance
  • Data Analysis & Decision Making
  • Leadership & Team Collaboration
); export default About;
